to offer you a trade.

10:02.272 --> 10:05.524
Last remnants of Karen's café
for Lydia -- straight up.

10:05.592 --> 10:07.226
Oh, I don't know.
That's tempting.

10:07.277 --> 10:09.895
I'll throw in my car.

10:09.946 --> 10:11.947
And my sunglasses.

10:12.032 --> 10:13.566
Car has new tires,
but that's it.

10:13.633 --> 10:15.234
Hmm. What do you say?

10:15.285 --> 10:16.902
Say "no deal."

10:16.953 --> 10:18.654
Say yes!
"No deal! I like it here!"

10:18.738 --> 10:20.456
Sorry.

10:20.540 --> 10:23.209
Fine. You can
have the sign anyway.

10:23.276 --> 10:25.911
I know Karen's
meant a lot to you, too.

10:25.962 --> 10:28.631
Oh, thank you so much.
I always wanted that.

10:30.717 --> 10:32.468
Yeah. Hi!

10:32.552 --> 10:34.786
I'm getting so sad today.

10:34.838 --> 10:35.921
