10:35.972 --> 10:39.175
I was thinking about
the Rivercourt,

10:39.259 --> 10:40.976
and now this sign.

10:41.061 --> 10:42.394
I just feel like

10:42.462 --> 10:44.463
it's the end of something
really good, you know?

10:44.514 --> 10:45.731
Makes me sad.

10:45.798 --> 10:48.567
Well, on the upside,
Lydia and I talked,

10:48.635 --> 10:49.852
and she told me

10:49.936 --> 10:53.355
that she wants to spend
every weekend in New York,

10:53.440 --> 10:54.824
shopping and seeing plays...

10:54.908 --> 10:56.325
...And hanging out with her Aunt Brooke.
Ohh.

10:56.409 --> 10:58.077
Huh?

10:58.144 --> 10:59.111
Yes.

10:59.162 --> 11:01.080
