She didn't even have you a week ago!

11:22.802 --> 11:24.203
Ohh!
I know!

11:26.339 --> 11:27.940
It wasn't you.

11:28.007 --> 11:29.441
It was Ian.

11:29.509 --> 11:32.177
It doesn't matter.
I resigned.

11:32.229 --> 11:34.530
To cover for your son.

11:34.614 --> 11:35.614
Why?

11:35.682 --> 11:38.450
Because he's my son.

11:38.518 --> 11:40.870
But your career.

11:40.954 --> 11:42.538
30 years,
Professor Kellerman.

11:44.741 --> 11:47.192
Well, <i>Mr.</i> Kellerman now.

11:47.244 --> 11:49.962
