<i>why</i> I did it,

11:50.029 --> 11:53.165
not whether or not
he was worth it.

11:56.219 --> 11:58.888
I haven't had a drink
since my wife died.

12:02.425 --> 12:03.875
We're fathers, Nathan.

12:03.927 --> 12:05.978
