I got to go to the bathroom.

14:26.808 --> 14:28.475
I told you
about that root beer.

14:28.526 --> 14:30.861
Don't make me tell Alex
about the camping trip.

14:30.945 --> 14:32.178
Shut up!

14:33.781 --> 14:35.549
Stinking drag-leg Laura!

14:35.616 --> 14:38.118
What?

14:38.185 --> 14:39.569
Sorry.

14:39.654 --> 14:41.238
No, it's okay.
He's cute.

14:41.322 --> 14:42.289
Kind of.

14:42.356 --> 14:43.523
So, what's up?

14:43.591 --> 14:46.209
I need a favor.

14:46.294 --> 14:47.861
