15:34.942 --> 15:36.910
Yeah.

15:41.632 --> 15:44.083
That's amazing.

15:44.135 --> 15:45.435
How long?

15:45.520 --> 15:48.355
I don't know. I mean,
it's different for everyone.

15:48.422 --> 15:49.823
Can you risk it?

15:49.891 --> 15:52.592
